<p>Create sections if you want students to register for a specific section, for grading or 
  other administrative purposes.</p>
 
<ol>
  <li>Click <strong>New Section</strong>.</li>
  <p>
  <li>Enter section name and click <strong>Create Section</strong>.</li>
  <p>
  <li>Click <strong>Section List</strong> to view sections.</li>
  <p>
  <li>To rename a section: hover mouse over section name. When icons appear, click
     <strong>pencil icon</strong> to enter new name.</li>
     <%= image_tag("edit_section.png", {:border => 1, :width => "40%", 
       :title=>"edit section"})%>
  <li>To delete a section: move mouse over section name. When icons appear, click
     <strong>trash icon</strong> to delete section.</li>
       <%= image_tag("trash_section.png", {:border => 1, :width => "30%", 
          :title=>"delete section"})%>
</ol>
